===================================
Solving Systems of Linear Equations                               [TOC]
===================================

In this example we solve a system of linear equations $Ax = b$ were the
coefficient matrix is general, i.e. not necessarily symmetric.  We solve the
system with __lapack::sv__ whcih is the FLENS port of LAPACK's __dgesv__.

:links:  __lapack::sv__  -> file:flens/lapack/gesv/sv.h
         __dgesv__       -> file:flens/lapack/interface/ref_lapack/dgesv.f


